title: Little Mix's Perrie Edwards isn't dating TOWIE's Joey Essex
text:
15:51   Google+ Perrie Edwards and Joey Essex have shot down rumours that they are dating.Reports suggested that the two singletons had hooked up, but the story has been denied by both parties. 
© WENN "Perrie is not dating Joey," a representative for the Little Mix star told MailOnline .Joey's spokesperson added: "Joey Essex exchanged numbers with Perrie Edwards at the Pride of Britain Awards and met up a couple of times. However, Joey is single." 
© Lime Pictures Perrie dated and was engaged to former One Direction member Zayn Malik until earlier this year .Meanwhile, Joey was in a relationship with Charlotte Stuchfield but they reportedly broke up in recent weeks.
